high_descs: Walk to the wall then turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and pick up the potato that's in there in the back right corner of the shelf with the lettuce.
Turn left and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to the sink and turn right to face it when you get there.
Wash the potato in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.

Put the potato under the loaf of bread.
